[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about whether Native Image automatically registers ServiceLoader providers. This seems like an important feature because it could streamline the deployment process for applications. If it's doing this without manual intervention, that would be super helpful for developers. I wonder if there are specific configurations or caveats to be aware of. I'll look into the documentation to clarify how this works and what the requirements might be.
