[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating native image initialization**\n\nI’m thinking about how a native image probably initializes many JDK classes at build time, like `java.text.DecimalFormatSymbols`. But can a system property be baked in at that time? If the `LocaleProviderAdapter` is initialized at build time without the property, it seems like static properties at runtime could come too late. I wonder if the native image initializes `sun.util.locale.provider.LocaleProviderAdapter` at runtime instead? That might be a concern.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0d993e88d0f5f73a016a0e6871a054819dab74f8066c186351\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqDmh_NRNsrFh9zn3zVAwSSkDDwUrkvleCn2qpG4VAOdqZ2-qAfgHpB_BU8UxN23Lg0uCSnFcRU02rSulFu9Oo6euVgpe8YplAZCrua0XtxwQ8rkZ3QrPaHYymt7FOTxsI5pFOPfJj4gK7AAIUBF0WECfPK77vjFAs6Z0n3rd65NO6G84H-JQbAxVPeY1wXkY7rv2GqD8JMNS0v5maEghol0XIomxWYMjwbnBldl9VVt9Z6vSq70ROdsolzphypwjDToYGeLHX-KjoXDK3MhEpssXJUHjUld9YsB1XkSueB3ebQDHSx4QXyBAWJgRrhwYOiFs16Ct9IzeeP4vKU9zwxOPglqvMqvymg-FIgZyv9GlAoowo9B2XQ33A50R8Ytm9hl4ZWTuV6b1JWgcYHgowFYONHhgK_HytsXDrh2q0Z4WoTolmx1pPGXLneLm6QiTdKOrjrIRDF6c46JHdo3hfIcKYeTjdy1zpNOnjpJCs-mxmLdTRXSbTzUvxbmlvlwxPYVl0ioWI2twuFniWGgZoLrsaOHWaksZJE7FEcqbsj0xl1wcU2u_gh5uoCV9BNcU8_GuCRMVI2mGkBJHPTceONVX4tReA26nJkmc5F1nVN_m9DBV3rrBPstGTiI02FA75w1juDlpN2Wgw4cb5kGVaMLESmt2yNTH-am37_NsjaeZ78e6mtlqtmjWyIVGOpupZ9O3r45nQ3IOF9aZ5rcjOSBCvRWtBEi9i5MnsL5fRUm5RBwp9_nXsf3SiKyAA4o29Et1SG1q1M8tMkCyyPfw91HBahZo9G121ltM7JONeOKfdMBglZhoQMRc6iez2XDtFW5zK7SSaRFeQ5QvUfWnejuNKntx-nrftpcKqY6FBxktnzBqpSybaYRhd8IulMfmLCdkcVY4iH5bqIBhUKt-0MxUPQ4ymiGbcOjkSX_GlFhslKRE1YiHKuXhpP-IjkNfW2udEHGYh_P3OyOP1k2HbFWXRJ7QVIoL2impCk7ZD1aJ3VyYwql5D0ppoED4X1Po0UwHZWB2kz7P2vcWe2Y0RiQDCAu4B3rwWulUHqzv5ghMff3gdnZL72CxALwS3my6XRvbFYRyPE3KRrx1hpuu8SQIyLF3vd_6DlXu1aA2wpweEPLhD4UreqI63JEM-jUdZWUuphslgFDG6dRZ_2iij3aMhAd4Eo6__pWKOT9HHAn5kZ-WuKvQv6fM8dTAY5ZLizbIa7BrUjOjrJtvUGI-9e2l